channel.title: What happened?
channel.description: I've left the community roughly 2 months(or longer, i cant remember) ago, and i've came back today and noticed there were a lot of big changes in the community. I was scouting servers and i have noticed that the amount of players on servers has decreased, alot. Also, i took note that many of the servers seem to be just downloaded, and the name changed, then ran on a dedicated (or none dedi) host. And i also see that the RSCD source has been leaked? Can someone please fill me in on some details that i might have missed?
